3:34','2018-10-30 10:14:02',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 10:14:02'),(3,6,30,'Q: How do I know my refund status?','<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Please visit&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/en\" style=\"color: rgb(162, 56, 105); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/en&nbsp;</a><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">and choose the option &quot;application status&quot; you&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; will need to input your refund tracking number or your PNR/Booking number.</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p>','                        Please visit https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/en and choose the option \"application status\" you                     will need to input your refund tracking number or your PNR/Booking number.','2018-10-30 10:19:07','2018-10-30 10:32:39',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 10:32:39'),(4,6,30,'Q: Do I need to complete my refund request prior to the original flight departure?','<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Not necessary. But please visit&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/en\" style=\"color: rgb(162, 56, 105); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/en&nbsp;</a><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">to submit the refund request&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; within 14 days.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p>','                        Not necessary. But please visit https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/en to submit the refund request                     within 14 days.','2018-10-30 10:37:37','2018-10-30 10:38:37',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 10:38:37'),(5,6,30,'Q: I cannot perform the change date / change route request in MMB. What can I do?','<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Currently all change requests except refund needs to be handled via our call centre.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p>','                        Currently all change requests except refund needs to be handled via our call centre.','2018-10-30 10:39:01','2018-10-30 10:39:04',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 10:39:01'),(6,6,30,'Q: How Can I Check the Latest Flight Status During a Typhoon?','<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">You can check the latest departure flight status on the official website of Hong Kong International Airport&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/sc/flights/departures/passenger.page\" style=\"color: rgb(162, 56, 105); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/sc/flights/departures/passenger.page&nbsp;</a><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">) Or you may also check&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the “Important Travel Notice” on HK Express official website.</span></p>','                        You can check the latest departure flight status on the official website of Hong Kong International Airport                     ( https://www.hongkongairport.com/sc/flights/departures/passenger.page ) Or you may also check                     the “Important Travel Notice” on HK Express official website.','2018-10-30 10:39:48','2018-10-30 10:40:20',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 10:40:20'),(7,6,30,'Q: My flight was cancelled due to typhoon. Can I make a free change to the next available flight online or via call center?','<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">Yes. Our Customer service agents will assist you change your booking to the next available flight. You may also contact us via online chat (&nbsp;<a href=\"ht