bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Aside from calling our hotline you may also contact us via online chat (&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.hkexpress.com/zh-cn/need-help/contact\" style=\"color: rgb(162, 56, 105); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">https://www.hkexpress.com/zh-cn/</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.hkexpress.com/zh-cn/need-help/contact\" style=\"color: rgb(162, 56, 105); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;need-help/contact&nbsp;</a><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">) to process your free flight change request. Our Customer service agents will assist you</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;change your booking to the next available flight. Please note that seats are subject to availability.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p>','                        Aside from calling our hotline you may also contact us via online chat ( https://www.hkexpress.com/zh-cn/                    need-help/contact ) to process your free flight change request. Our Customer service agents will assist you                    change your booking to the next available flight. Please note that seats are subject to availability.','2018-10-30 10:43:08','2018-10-30 10:43:25',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 10:43:25'),(10,6,30,'Q: My flight was delayed/cancelled. How can I apply for a flight delay/cancellation certificate?','<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">You can send an email to guest.relations@hkexpress.com to request a flight delay/cancellation certificate.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p>','                        You can send an email to guest.relations@hkexpress.com to request a flight delay/cancellation certificate.','2018-10-30 10:43:45','2018-10-30 10:43:59',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 10:43:59'),(11,6,31,'Q: Can I change the date/time of my flight?','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/162797360\" width=\"580\" height=\"218\" frameborder=\"0\" align=\"\"></iframe></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">Yes, you can change the date/time of your flight as long as you meet these 2 criteria:</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">1. Be sure to select a departure date and time at least 48 hours from now.</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181030/1540867676234003509.png\" title=\"1540867676234003509.png\" alt=\"flight1_01_en_dt.png\" width=\"828\" height=\"235\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">2. A fee will be charged for flight changes on a per Guest and per segment basis. Fare difference&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;may apply&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">and there will not be any refunds for lower fares. Please refer to this link&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(http://www.hkexpress.com/en-hk/plan/our-fares/our-fees) for the updated fees and charges.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181030/1540867944449037981.png\" title=\"1540867944449037981.png\" alt=\"1540867944449037981.png\" width=\"828\" height=\"79\"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">You can either use our mobile application, contact our call centre 48 hours before departure, leave us a message on live chat OR visit our website at www.hkexpress.com to submit any changes.</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">If you made your reservation through our website, you can conveniently change your flight on your own terms using the &quot;Manage My Booking&quot; feature. Just follow these simple steps:</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">Step 1. On your browser, type www.hkexpress.com then click &quot;Manage My Booking&quot;.</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181030/1540867965789032694.png\" title=\"1540867965789032694.png\" alt=\"flight1_03_en_dt.png\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Step 2. To retrieve your reservation, input your reference number and email address.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181030/1540868077570017119.png\" title=\"1540868077570017119.png\" alt=\"flight1_04_en_dt.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Step 3. Click the &quot;Change Flight&quot; button.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181030/1540868151266038310.png\" title=\"1540868151266038310.png\" alt=\"flight1_05_en_dt.png\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-ser