nt-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">As you select the flight you want, any additional charges will be displayed on the right side of your screen under booking summary.</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">After carefully reviewing the flight details and charges, you may now proceed with the payment. Input your credit card details. We accept Visa and Mastercard. Tick the box stating that you accept our Terms and Conditions. Click “Purchase” to confirm and submit the payment.</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">You now have successfully changed your flight. Kindly wait for the updated itinerary to be sent to your email address.</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181030/1540868326180097864.png\" title=\"1540868326180097864.png\" alt=\"flight1_08_en_dt.png\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></span></span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p>','Yes, you can change the date/time of your flight as long as you meet these 2 criteria:1. Be sure to select a departure date and time at least 48 hours from now.                        2. A fee will be charged for flight changes on a per Guest and per segment basis. Fare difference                         may apply and there will not be any refunds for lower fares. Please refer to this link                         (http://www.hkexpress.com/en-hk/plan/our-fares/our-fees) for the updated fees and charges.You can either use our mobile application, contact our call centre 48 hours before departure, leave us a message on live chat OR visit our website at www.hkexpress.com to submit any changes.If you made your reservation through our website, you can conveniently change your flight on your own terms using the \"Manage My Booking\" feature. Just follow these simple steps:Step 1. On your browser, type www.hkexpress.com then click \"Manage My Booking\".                            Step 2. To retrieve your reservation, input your reference number and email address.                            Step 3. Click the \"Change Flight\" button.                            Step 4. Tick the desired flight sector you wish to change and choose the new desired flight date.                         To confirm, click \"Change Flight\".                        Step 5. On this screen, you will see all the available flight options. Please choose the new desired flight                     schedule then click \"Change Booking\".As you select the flight you want, any additional charges will be displayed on the right side of your screen under booking summary.After carefully reviewing the flight details and charges, you may now proceed with the payment. Input 