oma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/166925725\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" align=\"\"></iframe></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">可以。您可以在滿足以下兩個條件的情況下更改航班的日期/時間:</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">1.在航班起飛48個小時前</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181109/1541754472073031865.png\" title=\"1541754472073031865.png\" alt=\"flight1_01_hk_dt.png\"/></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">2.將根據每位旅客訂購的票價類型收取更改手續費。 更改航班可能產生票價差額的情況，如欲更改的票價比原票價低， 其差額將不會退還。 請瀏覽以下網址(http://www.hkexpress.com/zh-hk/plan/our-fares/our-fees) 查詢最新票價及收費。</span></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181109/1541754497820023556.png\" title=\"1541754497820023556.png\" alt=\"flight1_02_hk_dt.png\"/></span></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">旅客如欲更改航班，可於航班起飛48小時前透過手機應用程式、聯絡我們的客戶服務熱線、透過實時通訊留言或於網頁www.hkexpress.com提交更改。</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">若您計劃預定航班 ，我們建議您在較早的時間預定，以享受最低票價及優惠推廣。但幾位數量及票價隨時間浮動。</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">預定行程，只需跟從以下步驟：</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">步驟1. 選擇航班</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181109/1541754533284062751.png\" title=\"1541754533284062751.png\" alt=\"flight1_03_hk_dt.png\"/></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">步驟2.輸入訂單編號及電郵地址以搜索訂位。</span></span><br/></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181109/1541754547430029242.png\" title=\"