lection.                                Step 4. Select your seat by clicking the boxes. To proceed, click \"Add to Booking\" button.                                     Kindly take note of the following conditions if you wish to choose a seat in an exit row:                                    Step 5. After carefully reviewing the charges, you may now proceed with the payment.                                 Input your credit card details. We accept Visa and Mastercard. Then tick the box stating that                                 you accept our Terms and Conditions. Click \"Next\" to proceed.                                You have successfully selected your seat assignment! Just kindly wait for your updated travel itinerary.                               REMINDER:                              Bookings purchased from our guest relations or from a travel agency cannot use the \"Manage My Booking\"                               feature. If you want to pre-book your seat, please contact our hotline for further assistance. Please make                               sure your flight is still at least 3 hours prior to departure time.','2018-10-30 12:12:03','2018-10-30 12:12:05',1,1,1,'2018-10-30 12:12:03'),(29,6,33,'Q: How can I check-in using web browser?','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/162494270\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" align=\"\"></iframe></p><p><br/></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">We offer different check-in options for your seamless flying experience. You can either check-in online, at our airport counters or even in-town.</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">For more reference:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hkexpress.com/en-hk/plan/flying-with-us/check-iN\" style=\"color: rgb(162, 56, 105); text-decoration-line: none;\">https://www.hkexpress.com/en-hk/plan/flying-with-us/check-iN</a></p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(153, 0, 153); font-weight: bold;\">Online Check-in</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">Online check-in opens 48 hours before and closes 75 mins before scheduled departure time. If you do not have any check-in baggage, you can go straight to the gate with your mobile boarding pass and enjoy!&nbsp;For guests that need to check-in your baggage, please visit our online check-in counters at airports accordingly. Guests are reminded to arrive at the boarding gate at least 40 minutes before departure to prepare for boarding, and gate will be closed 20 minutes before departure.</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">Online Check-in is available for flights departing Hong Kong (except to Saipan), Japan, Thailand, Korea, Taiwan, Vietnam and Cambodia, between 75 minutes and 48 hours prior to departure. It is not available for bookings with infants and Guests that require assistance.</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\">Guests departing from Seoul, Busan, Jeju, Nha Trang, Danang, Hualien and Siem Reap must visit the check-in counter for travel document verification and to obtain a printed boarding pass before proceeding to immigration.</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-l