03_hk_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr><td class=\"rowheader\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">您亦可以點選下拉以檢閱行李費用。<br/>可點選添加餐點以購買機上餐點。</p></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542844597151044278.png\" title=\"1542844597151044278.png\" alt=\"flight9_04_hk_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr><td class=\"rowheader\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">您可以點選下方的空格以加入旅遊保險。 在輸入旅客姓名及附加服務後，點選繼續。</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">在下一視窗，您可以選擇指定座位。</p></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542844639971014744.png\" title=\"1542844639971014744.png\" alt=\"flight9_05_hk_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr><td class=\"rowheader\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">步驟3. 點選空格以選擇座位。點選繼續進行下一步。</p></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542844672012012363.png\" title=\"1542844672012012363.png\" alt=\"flight9_06_hk_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542844685170088252.png\" title=\"1542844685170088252.png\" alt=\"flight9_07_hk_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr><td class=\"rowheader\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; 