le=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">步骤2. 请输入旅客资料。旅客姓名需与护照上姓名一致。</p></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542846867907098181.png\" title=\"1542846867907098181.png\" alt=\"flight9_03_cn_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr><td class=\"rowheader\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">您亦可以点选下拉以检阅行李费用。<br/>可点选添加餐点以购买机上餐点。</p></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542846874666079546.png\" title=\"1542846874666079546.png\" alt=\"flight9_04_cn_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr><td class=\"rowheader\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">您可以点选下方的空格以加入旅游保险。 在输入旅客姓名及附加服务后，点选继续。</p><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">在下一视窗，您可以选择指定座位。</p></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542846882999035708.png\" title=\"1542846882999035708.png\" alt=\"flight9_05_cn_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr><td class=\"rowheader\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><p class=\"paragraphs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 115px; padding-right: 115px;\">步骤3. 点选空格以选择座位。点选继续进行下一步。</p></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px;\"><img src=\"/hkexpress/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181122/1542846893376064174.png\" title=\"1542846893376064174.png\" alt=\"flight9_06_cn_dt.png\"/></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td class=\"rowheader\" style=\"paddin